CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper August 12, 1961, pg. 20, reads: "Six Tan Aces in Jaycee All-Star Game - Western Squad - Coached by John Bruno of Sewickley Township High School, and Don Karanovich of Trafford High School, this hefty squad could prove difficult for the Allegheny entry to handle... - Harris photos."
TitMainTitle: Western Pennsylvania All-Star Jaycee football team with coaches John Bruno and Don Karanovich, posed on field
